BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (THE FORMULA: ACKNOWLEDGE + VALIDATE + REDIRECT) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (Step 1: ACKNOWLEDGE what they're doing/feeling) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.0 Td (Step 2: VALIDATE their emotion \(even if behavior isn't okay\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.0 Td (Step 3: REDIRECT to what they CAN do) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 638.2 Td (Example: 'I see you're throwing blocks \(acknowledge\). You're frustrated \(validate\). You) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 624.2 Td (can throw soft balls outside instead \(redirect\).') Tj ET
endstream
endobj
