stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (NOT LISTENING / IGNORING) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 680.2 Td (Instead of: 'How many times do I have to tell you?!') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 666.2 Td (Try: 'I need your eyes on me. I have something important to say.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 642.4 Td (Instead of: 'You never listen!') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 628.4 Td (Try: 'I notice you're focused on something else. I'll wait until you're ready.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 604.6 Td (Instead of: 'DO IT NOW!') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 590.6 Td (Try: 'This needs to happen before [next fun thing]. Would you like to do it now or in 2) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 576.6 Td (minutes?') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 552.8 Td (Instead of: 'Are you deaf?!') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 538.8 Td (Try: 'Let me come to you. [Touch shoulder, get on their level] Hey, I need your help with) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 524.8 Td (something.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 501.0 Td (Instead of: 'If I have to say this again...') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 487.0 Td (Try: 'I've asked once. I'm going to help you do it now.') Tj ET
endstream
endobj
