stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (HITTING / BITING / AGGRESSION) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 680.2 Td (Instead of: 'Stop hitting RIGHT NOW!') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 666.2 Td (Try: 'I won't let you hurt. Bodies are not for hitting. I'm going to keep everyone safe.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 642.4 Td (Instead of: 'We do NOT hit in this house!') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 628.4 Td (Try: 'You're so angry your body wants to hit. You CAN: stomp feet, squeeze a pillow, or) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 614.4 Td (punch this cushion.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 590.6 Td (Instead of: 'Say you're sorry!') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 576.6 Td (Try: 'Let's check on your brother. How can we help him feel better?') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 552.8 Td (Instead of: 'What is WRONG with you?') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 538.8 Td (Try: 'Something big is happening inside you. Let's figure out what you need.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 515.0 Td (Instead of: 'Go to your room!') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 501.0 Td (Try: 'Let's move to a calm space together until your body feels safe again.') Tj ET
endstream
endobj
