stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (BEDTIME BATTLES) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 680.2 Td (Instead of: 'Get in bed NOW!') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 666.2 Td (Try: 'It's time for our bedtime routine. Would you like to start with books or pajamas?') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 642.4 Td (Instead of: 'I don't care if you're not tired!') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 628.4 Td (Try: 'Your body needs rest to grow. You don't have to sleep yet - just rest quietly.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 604.6 Td (Instead of: 'This is the LAST time I'm coming in!') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 590.6 Td (Try: 'I'll check on you one more time in 5 minutes. You're safe.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 566.8 Td (Instead of: 'If you don't stay in bed...') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 552.8 Td (Try: 'Your bed is your cozy spot. If you need me, I'm right here.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 529.0 Td (Instead of: 'ENOUGH stalling!') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 515.0 Td (Try: 'I know you want more time with me. Let's have our special bedtime chat and then) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 501.0 Td (lights out.') Tj ET
endstream
endobj
