BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (SIBLING FIGHTING) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 680.2 Td (Instead of: 'STOP FIGHTING!') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 666.2 Td (Try: 'I see two people who need help solving a problem. What happened?') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 642.4 Td (Instead of: 'Who started it?') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 628.4 Td (Try: 'It doesn't matter who started it. How can we fix it?') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 604.6 Td (Instead of: 'Share or I'll take it away!') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 590.6 Td (Try: 'You're both using this. How should we solve it? Timer? Trade?') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 566.8 Td (Instead of: 'Be nice to your sister!') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 552.8 Td (Try: 'I hear unkind words. In this family, we speak with respect. Try again.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 529.0 Td (Instead of: 'That's IT, both of you go to your rooms!') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 515.0 Td (Try: 'You both need a break. Take 5 minutes apart, then let's solve this together.') Tj ET
endstream
