BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (HOMEWORK / SCHOOL REFUSAL) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 680.2 Td (Instead of: 'Just DO your homework!') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 666.2 Td (Try: 'Homework feels hard today. What part feels most overwhelming? Let's start with just) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 652.2 Td (ONE problem.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 628.4 Td (Instead of: 'You're being lazy!') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 614.4 Td (Try: 'I can see you're stuck. Would you like help getting started, or do you need a) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 600.4 Td (10-minute break first?') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 576.6 Td (Instead of: 'You're going to fail!') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 562.6 Td (Try: 'Struggling means you're learning something new. I believe you can figure this out.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 538.8 Td (Instead of: 'No TV until homework is done!') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 524.8 Td (Try: 'Homework first, then fun stuff! How about we set a timer for 20 minutes of focused) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 510.8 Td (work?') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 487.0 Td (Instead of: 'You HAVE to go to school!') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 473.0 Td (Try: 'I hear you don't want to go. What's making school hard right now? Let's) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 459.0 Td (problem-solve together.') Tj ET
endstream
endobj
