20 0 obj
<< /Length 1041 >>
stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (REPAIR SCRIPTS \(When YOU Lose Your Cool\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (You WILL yell sometimes. You're human. Here's how to repair:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 666.2 Td (  * 'I yelled and I'm sorry. That wasn't okay. You didn't deserve that.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 652.2 Td (  * 'I got really frustrated and I handled it badly. I'm working on doing better.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 638.2 Td (  * 'Even grownups have big feelings sometimes. I should have taken a deep breath.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 624.2 Td (  * 'I love you. My anger was about MY problem, not about you being bad.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 610.2 Td (  * 'Can we have a redo? Let me try that conversation again the right way.') Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 586.4 Td (Repair teaches your child: mistakes happen, relationships matter more than perfection, and) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 572.4 Td (it's brave to apologize.) Tj ET
54 552.4 m 558 552.4 l 0.5 w S
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 542.4 Td (By Daniel Tesfamariam | Calm parents raise calm kids. You've got this.) Tj ET
endstream
